'''Imuhaγ''' d agdud [[Imaziγen|amaziγ]] yettidiren deg [[Aneεruf|Uneεruf]] n [[tafriqt]]. Akal-nsen d Aneεruf (Idurar n [[Tasili]], n Ayer di [[Niger]], atg.)

Yernu imi ay zgan tddun af udar, ttreggizen (teddun) nitni d lmal-nsen (iγersiwen n-sen d ileγman) seg wemkan γer wayed', wwd'en γer wat'as n tmiwa di [[Tafriqt|Tefriqt]]. Imuhaγ xuld'en at'as n yegduden ifriqiyen ay ten-id-iqerben neγ yellan γer tama n-sen, nitni fkan-asen daγ-nni wwin-d at'as seg-sen. Ass-a, nezmer ad naf Imuhaγ di Niger d [[Mali|Mali]], am wakken  nezmer ad naf kra n trebbaɛ-nsen neγ n waggayen (groups) di [[Čadd]], Burkina Faso akk d Nigeria. 

Deg wend'ul n Uneεruf (Niger akk d Mali), at'as n yegduden ifriqiyen ay yettidiren γer tama n Yimuhaγ, nezmer ad d-nebder seg-sen [[Ibambaraten]], [[Ifularen]] akk d [[Isarakuliyen|Yisarakuliyen]]. Kra seg yegduden-agi kessen lmal am Yimuhaɣ, di lweqt i deg wiyad' xeddmen tafellah't neγ akal. Tuγ (yella), wakal n wenẓul n Uneεruf kkan (uγent) deg-s isaffen, d aya ay t-yerran d agilal, amakken (meh'sub) yelha (igarrez) i tfellah't. 

